title: Frankie Valli tribute act to play The Burt
text:
What’s being touted as America’s top Frankie Valli tribute show is coming to The Burt early next year. 

Tribute band Let’s Hang On! will play the Burton Cummings Theatre on Jan. 15. The stage show features all of the Four Season’s greatest hits, while also paying tribute to Broadway show The Jersey Boys. 
Tickets for the show range from $29.50 to $79.50 and go on sale to the general public Friday via Ticketmaster. Sponsored Links Frankie Valli tribute act to play The Burt
